title: Looking for Duo Que partner for first 10 games.
body:
I Recently Moved To OCE from EUW.
Didn't know you lose your champion mastery,
rank, honors and match history when you move.
Need someone to help me skate past the first 10 games so i get a good starting rank.
Please add me in game if you would like to help.
Much Appreciated.
~Bespooks

-Edit, Champions I play are {{champion:119}} {{champion:222}} {{champion:25}} {{champion:45}} {{champion:115}} {{champion:101}} {{champion:110}} {{champion:29}} {{champion:41}} {{champion:9}}
Prefer to play support or mid lane but can top and adc too.
(I have no match history because of the reset)

replies.body: My Profile looks like i'm a complete noob because my stuff is not saved between server changes.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}  Rito pls fix this! It would be super awesome if all your champion masteries and ranks got transferred too! :c
